metadata.name: aNteFuturism - MANIFESTO
metadata.description:
aNteFuTurism is an artistic movement involving nostalgia, absurd, and blockchain technology. 
Using NFT as a medium it aims to be an ode to the disappearance of the old world while addressing the digitalization of our surroundings. 

This is our Manifesto

www.antefuturism.art
